    "name": "Hellfire Poncho",
    "steam_appid": 3017150,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017150/extras/f8e442b882362dd91e71eea2af134bcb.avif?t=1771871559\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017150/extras_big/f8e442b882362dd91e71eea2af134bcb.avif?t=1771871559 width=800 height=542 /></span>The <strong>definitive</strong> western poncho roguelite experience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Embark on a trip through hell as Poncho Rodriguez, the most ruthless outlaw from the Wild West.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Go on a rampage while enjoying the dynamic electro-western music.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Meet creatures that will try to help or (and) kill you and reclaim what you were stolen...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build your best card deck which you can bet on the saloon in a surreal <strong>dice poker game.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017150/extras/4ece418b42411e55fd6964a1edd0d27d.avif?t=1771871559\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017150/extras_big/4ece418b42411e55fd6964a1edd0d27d.avif?t=1771871559 width=800 height=197 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017150/extras/d69ebb4133ac7607aa90d5067bb9d632.poster.avif?t=1771871559\" width=616 height=215 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017150/extras/d69ebb4133ac7607aa90d5067bb9d632.webm?t=1771871559\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Upgrades come in the shape of cards. Choose thoughtfully and prepare yourself for the next levels.</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Weapon cards: Reveal unique weapons with different play styles.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Upgrade cards: Upgrade your stats and modify your weapons to the limit.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dice: Gather different special dice to increase your chances in the poker game.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collectibles: Find these rare collectibles to learn about Poncho's story...</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017150/extras/eb65d95bc58532a8d2e7e5050c214278.avif?t=1771871559\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017150/extras_big/eb65d95bc58532a8d2e7e5050c214278.avif?t=1771871559 width=800 height=197 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017150/extras/a4d27a9e33a0f74f1098bd7db5f1bb8b.poster.avif?t=1771871559\" width=616 height=215 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017150/extras/a4d27a9e33a0f74f1098bd7db5f1bb8b.webm?t=1771871559\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>Try your luck on a dice game against the fellows you find in the saloon, make your build even stronger, or start from zero.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017150/extras/219ef915f03d27c89579b1eede5a3669.avif?t=1771871559\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017150/extras_big/219ef915f03d27c89579b1eede5a3669.avif?t=1771871559 width=800 height=197 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017150/extras/25e538722f85cefde82a0f4ff4fb577f.poster.avif?t=1771871559\" width=616 height=215 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017150/extras/25e538722f85cefde82a0f4ff4fb577f.webm?t=1771871559\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Apply modifications to your weapons, go for a hell-destructive build covering the whole level in bullets, or you may prefer to go slowly with your sniper shooting from afar...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Keep the cards you liked for the next run or use them to get better ones at the saloon.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build your strategy through runs and don't be afraid to start again.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017150/extras/3ddc5c15bede72cf2ca183feb2448d95.avif?t=1771871559\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017150/extras_big/3ddc5c15bede72cf2ca183feb2448d95.avif?t=1771871559 width=800 height=197 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017150/extras/e3b8d4e541d41dd40d438ea13cee3fec.avif?t=1771871559\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017150/extras_big/e3b8d4e541d41dd40d438ea13cee3fec.avif?t=1771871559 width=800 height=279 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017150/extras/10c412537b50bdd1aea570044cb498ab.avif?t=1771871559\" width=616 height=244 /></span></p>",
